Europe won back the crown after the team of Danish captain Thomas Bjorn scored the 14.5 points it needed to defeat the US.
American star Phil Mickelson, who had problems over much of the tournament, sunk his tee on the 16th track (par 3) in the water and lost to Francesco Molinari.
